headline: Prudential expands collaboration with Workday to deliver a seamless, personalized benefits experience through Workday Wellness
summary: NEWARK, N.J., February 27, 2025--Prudential Financial, Inc. (NYSE: PRU) announced today an expanded strategic relationship with Workday Inc. that harnesses the power of data and AI to help employers better tailor their benefits programs to meet the needs of their workforce.
